{"tid":1701507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史上的大罷工，如省港大罷工，其實很多都係靠罷工組織強迫人唔返工，你敢返工就打9你甚至殺左你而達成！","createTime":"2019-11-09T06:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T15:09:58.000Z","uid":118346,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"deed04152a15f6fa735e49e0b647d4483421bb62","tid":1701507,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"from facebook friend :<br />\n<br />\n見到有人問搞總罷工點解o甘難。呢個問題之所以成為問題，系因為我地睇太多童話化消過毒的19歷史。歷史上的大罷工，如省港大罷工, 其實很多都係靠罷工組織強迫人唔返工，你敢返工就打9你甚至殺左你而達成的。美國其中一個罷工鬥爭最成功的工會teamster，系同意大利黑手黨一夥的。香港地，你擋吓地鐵畀人鬧吓就討論應唔應該阻人返工，真係收皮啦。<br />\n<br />\n人地西方國家罷工，最緊要系組糾察線（picket line），唔系和理非篤勇武灰，而系封廠唔畀人返工，你敢越過糾察線返工就打9你。<a href=\"https://money.howstuffworks.com/strike3.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.howstuffworks.com%2Fstrike3.htm&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOEXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=f50bb653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.howstuffworks.com/strike3.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4172d0ebc88cbcebfdde7fb77975363206f4a2ab","tid":1701507,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"呢樣眞"},{"pid":"b5a87150063f376d198c2990bf1078e7f49f9712","tid":1701507,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71a3eb2366b2c342135e1c4ecc3b9aa55d0d47a","tid":1701507,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ceba8f41492ef2dbf124b97629643a1eb4bc37e","tid":1701507,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87176cbfa6d5611500b69464832f64ea2b78fbe2","tid":1701507,"uid":81273,"like":0